nsp.impl.random

Class RandomGenerator_Exponential

  • java.lang.Object
    • nsp.impl.random.RandomGenerator_Exponential
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, RandomGenerator

    public class RandomGenerator_Exponential
extends java.lang.Object
implements RandomGenerator, java.lang.Cloneable
    Number generator that implements the RandomGenerator interface, and returns pseudo-random numbers drawn from an exponential distribution. This class is primarily a wrapper for the Colt package's Exponential class.
